---
title: Pearled Couscous Salad with Citrus & Fennel
description: Fennel and orange is a classic flavor combo. Pearled couscous is the perfect base for refreshing herbs, salty feta, and crunchy pepitas.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/54d3d0b16ced6e64348b4569.jpg
